    <measure>Postoperative pain scores of periarticular injection and fascia block for total knee arthroplasty</measure>
    <time_frame>postoperative 24 hours</time_frame>
    <description>Patients were assigned in two groups to perform either periarticular injection (group PI) and fascia block ( group FB). They were accessed by visual analog scale. The aim was to compare the efficacy and side effects of periarticular injection and fascia block.</description>
